00:09:01.900 --> 00:09:03.480
And so when you were sitting next

00:09:03.480 --> 00:09:05.670
to me just chatting I had
no idea you were going

00:09:05.670 --> 00:09:08.370
to say all these nice
things about me, thank you.

00:09:08.370 --> 00:09:12.690
I've learned my lesson the last
