really patient with me.

00:52:51.590 --> 00:52:53.510
I obviously could go
on for six hours.

00:52:53.510 --> 00:52:58.140
[ Applause ]

00:52:58.140 --> 00:52:59.600
Yes, there's a question.

00:52:59.600 --> 00:53:00.900
